title: Main Supp LF Team (Former Plat1)
body:
Aus dem englischen Bereich von EUW ein Copy Paste von mir :) 

Hi!

Currently I am looking for a team to improve since it is a bit harder to climb divisions as a main supp only :) I dont want to keep playing the "you win some, you lose some"-thing...

So here are the facts:

currently stuck in Gold 2 (started S7 two weeks ago), should be Plat at the end of this week
playing since S3
large Support-Championpool
always tryhard...you play to win the game
able to analyze own mistakes
the wish to become a better player
If you have questions, just write me ingame or here!

so far

cheerz, Doc
